<li><a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/6645">Auto-generate completions</a>
<ul>
<li>Blocked on <a href="https://github.com/clap-rs/clap/issues/3166">clap-rs/clap#3166</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Generalize cargo's test assertion code
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3946">Add <code>CARGO_WORKSPACE_DIR</code></a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/assert-rs/trycmd/issues/221">Inline snapshotting in snapbox</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/assert-rs/trycmd/issues/92">Structured assertions in snapbox</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/assert-rs/trycmd/issues/151">Find a solution for order-independent assertions between cargo and snapbox</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Needs design and/or experimentation:</p>
